<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>You're Invited to Join <%= @team.name %>!</h1>
    <p>
      Hello, you've been invited to join the team <strong><%= @team.name %></strong> by 
      <%= @invitation.sender.email %>. Click the button below to accept the invitation and create your account.
    </p>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 20px;">
      <a href="<%= @url %>" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
        Accept Invitation
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><%= @url %></p>

    <p>Thank you!</p>
  </body>
</html>
